{"tid":1361423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一群熱愛香港的漁護署職員的公開信","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T15:25:44.000Z","uid":147684,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8ce1fdce726d2c525cb3f34a61f5f2e2ba0fb32e","tid":1361423,"uid":147684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:08:37.000Z","msg":"致香港市民：<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群漁農自然護理署職員，一直低調地默默為環境、為市民服務。同時我們與香港大眾一樣，熱愛香港這片土地及給予我們生活的一切，包括家人、朋友與下一代。<br />\n<br />\n由612至今遊行時警方過份使用武力，及721元朗鄉黑暴力打傷市民，令社會各界相當震驚及憤怒。作為與民並肩的公僕，我們對政府管治不負責任的態度極度失望，破損香港長久艱辛累積的法治及和平聲譽，更甚把社會的撕裂尤其是警民關係推到極點。希望政府能有擔當具良知地正面回應社會長期的訴求，包括 ：<br />\n1. 撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義<br />\n3. 追究警隊濫權<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n此外，我們亦希望香港警隊能毋忘及確守其價值觀 -「以公正、無私和體諒的態度去處事和對人」，權在你手，行事要光明磊落，重建香港市民對你們的信任。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我們懇請香港廣大市民要愛惜自己，珍惜生命，表達意見之同時，亦要顧及自身安全，香港是我們的家，也是你們的家，各位的每一分力量雖微小但卻重要，少了誰，便成就不了美麗的香港！請你們繼續努力，我們會繼續堅守自己的崗位，亦會與大家繼續同行！<br />\n<br />\n一群熱愛香港的漁農自然護理署職員上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RiufqXU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRiufqXU.png&h=ae6f39b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U5s43KA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU5s43KA.png&h=608e4a02&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1xF6xCW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1xF6xCW.png&h=bcee25d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/faw5Obh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffaw5Obh.png&h=989cbaa6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GWnpjhY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGWnpjhY.png&h=2cf862d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X5871wj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5871wj.png&h=678bd25d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/24/230523_070fe772e1ab622a96159ddbd96bbcd6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F24%2F230523_070fe772e1ab622a96159ddbd96bbcd6.png&h=936c2fac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/24/230525_a940f29171e6bcf3ea660903c1419795.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F24%2F230525_a940f29171e6bcf3ea660903c1419795.png&h=5ad2e44c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/24/230529_467d74901df34010daa632e616e3a45e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F24%2F230529_467d74901df34010daa632e616e3a45e.png&h=d2aff519&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e060924a35deb0055a89bab923e88cedec9efb7a","tid":1361423,"uid":147684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:09:11.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075db50540fbbbb7105640e0097c1faecc796765","tid":1361423,"uid":45914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22a18ebd7382c80d55e39dcd842aef9adb8d1e57","tid":1361423,"uid":54243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:10:16.000Z","msg":"幫手放d 畜生入狗屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52111e8d5f2ba2b3b9b4e6767cf1b35f93bd1231","tid":1361423,"uid":168831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"cb5b2bc8c866a765e1630166b669e1429abc86ff","tid":1361423,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:13:35.000Z","msg":"唔好意思!!<br />\n後日0726就係機場集會!!!<br />\n機場有無數外國旅客!!!<br />\n係對外發出香港嘅SOS求救訊號嘅大好機會!!!<br />\n一定要搞大佢!!!<br />\n宜家一齊推&darr;&darr;&darr;<br />\n<br />\n[ 7.26 機場 ] 星期五放工入機場!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/13